						<summary><p>An Urdu-Tamil dictionary or vocabulary list, providing, for example:
<list>
									<item>A list of amounts in Anna (¹⁄₁₆ rupee) (<locus facs="17">U2, f1r, c1, 1</locus>).</item>
									<item>A list of numbers (<locus facs="24">U2, f2r, c3, 1</locus>).</item>
									<item>A list of the weekdays (<locus facs="32">U2, f8r, c3</locus>).</item>
									<item>A list of the months (<locus facs="33">U2, f8v, c1</locus>).</item>
									<item>Expressions for time (<locus facs="33">U2, f9r, c1, 4</locus>).</item>
									<item>A list of castes (<locus facs="34">U2, f9v</locus>).</item>
								</list></p>
